title: Battlestar Galactica - Six of One.S04E02.edshrinker.AVI
description:
Six of One

Episode Number: 63    Season Num: 4    First Aired: Friday April 11, 2008
Prod Code: n/a

The Cylons learn that the Final Five are in the Colonial fleet. Some of the Cylons want the Cavil model to stop lobotomizing the Raider ships.

Starbuck desperately tries to convince the others that the fleet is going the wrong way in their search for Earth.

Cast and Crew

Writer: 	Michael Angeli
Director: 	Anthony Hemingway
Star: 	Mary McDonnell (Laura Roslin),  Jamie Bamber (Lee "Apollo" Adama),  Katee Sackhoff (Kara "Starbuck" Thrace),  James Callis (Gaius Baltar),  Edward James Olmos (William Adama),  Tricia Helfer (Number Six/Caprica Six),  Grace Park (Sharon Valerii/Sharon "Athena" Agathon)

Notes
The episode title reflects the traditional idiom, "Six of one, half a dozen of the other." The phrase is used to point out that two differently named items or collections are really the same thing.

"Six of One" is also the name of the "Official Appreciation Society" for the cult favorite TV show The Prisoner (1967). Patrick McGoohan&#039;s character "No. 6" inspired the naming of the Battlestar Galactica character Number Six (played by Tricia Helfer).
